title: Riot Grrrl songs and some other related stuff
description:
This is a collection of Riot Grrrl songs I&#039;ve accumulated over the years. Riot Grrrl is an underground punk movement that started in the early 90&#039;s, and is associated with 3rd wave feminism. Riot Grrrl bands often address issues such as rape, domestic abuse, sexuality, and female empowerment. 

Not all of the bands I&#039;ve included are Riot Grrrl as they have little to do with punk but most of them deal with the afore mentioned issues. 

Enjoy!!
